_sText:
I made this map thinking about how to make rounded edges in walls, so an idea popped in my head, to make a medium sized city map. So I spent time on it with my studio, and this version 1 came to fininalize. 

Includes: 

- Buildings with Props, decals, lighting.
- Breakable Windows, Vents.
- Sounds.
- Fog.
- Various Camping Spots.
- Optimization.

Since this is only Version 1, I could make version 2 much bigger, or change alot of rooms and such.
